snippet: Americans Michael Thompson, Chris Kirk, Webb Simpson and Jordan Spieth reveled in a birdie fest as they charged into a tie for the lead in Friday's opening round of the Hyundai Tournament of Champions....

headline.print_headline: Thompson, Kirk, Simpson and Spieth Take Control in Hawaii
headline.main: Thompson, Kirk, Simpson and Spieth Take Control in Hawaii

lead_paragraph: Americans Michael Thompson, Chris Kirk, Webb Simpson and Jordan Spieth reveled in a birdie fest as they charged into a tie for the lead in Friday's opening round of the Hyundai Tournament of Champions.
